    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&quot;a Horror FPS, Hide &amp; Seek Game, essentially it's like a modern version of PacMan&quot;</strong></h2><br><strong><i>You are trapped in an abandoned arcade hall. The Ghosts of the Arcade, the good ones revealed to you what you have to do, to escape.<br>You gotta collect coins...<br>As long as you collect coins, you are vulnerable to the demonic presence that lingers in the arcade.</i></strong><br><br><strong><u><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The collected coins can be used to play real games on arcade machines.</h2></u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/c2b7a288589ed5265f1dc89bce0ce507.poster.avif?t=1666304913\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/c2b7a288589ed5265f1dc89bce0ce507.webm?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/c2b7a288589ed5265f1dc89bce0ce507.mp4?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><u>Play Games Like For Example:</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2d Fighter<br></li><li>Sidescroller<br></li><li>Shoot 'Em Up</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/63b7cd95a6a2a71c9776a27aa449bae9.poster.avif?t=1666304913\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/63b7cd95a6a2a71c9776a27aa449bae9.webm?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/63b7cd95a6a2a71c9776a27aa449bae9.mp4?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>While playing an arcade game your goal is to get a high score on the arcade machine. Once you get a high score, the Ghost of the Machine will reveal a secret message that you can use to open a safe or a locked door...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/f7ee198ee881220e47b3078adb11abd1.poster.avif?t=1666304913\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/f7ee198ee881220e47b3078adb11abd1.webm?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/f7ee198ee881220e47b3078adb11abd1.mp4?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>But be careful, the demonic presence is everywhere, it will surprise you by its appearance.<br>Watch out for sheets resembling the shape of a covered stool, chair or even a arcade machine. The demon is all around you, watching you.</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>So will you be able to get a high score to unlock your freedom?<br>Wishlist now and you'll be able to find out soon enough!</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/03a792c98a93f151bc64ac2f0c1f8ff4.poster.avif?t=1666304913\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1896370/extras/03a792c98a93f151bc64ac2f0c1f8ff4.webm?t=1666304913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>please Do Note:</u></strong></h2></h2>This game is a Work in Progress, the Screenshots you see are not representing the actual gameplay, they are just to fill the gap.<br>Updates will be made on a regular basis.<br>Thank you for your understanding and for the support",
